# Compose and manifests

- **Manifest**: `version: 1`, `template.id` / `template.title`, optional `core: false`, `priority` blocks with `type` in `stack-base` | `stack-extension` | `cross-cutting` and `modules` paths **without** `.md` under `modules/`.
- **Modules**: Top-level sections must use exactly `# Title` (one `#`). Nested content uses `##`+. No YAML front matter in `modules/` (compose v1).
- **Merge order**: `stack-base` < `stack-extension` < `cross-cutting`; duplicate `#` titles keep the higher-priority layer.
- **After edits**: `python scripts/compose.py --all` then `python scripts/compose.py --check` before committing.
